{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"identifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSURL","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"identifier","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A string that uniquely identifies the source in the style to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which it is added.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"configurationURL","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A URL to a TileJSON configuration file describing the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"source’s contents and other metadata.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An initialized raster tile source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:","type":"reference"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" documentation for more information about tile"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than the default, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:tileSize:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNRasterTileSource(im)initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"abstract":[{"text":"The proxy object for the current map style.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNStyle","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNStyle","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterStyleLayer":{"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer"},{"text":" is a style layer that renders georeferenced raster","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"imagery on the map, especially raster tiles.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNRasterStyleLayer","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNRasterStyleLayer","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrasterstylelayer"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource":{"title":"MLNRasterTileSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNRasterTileSource","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"},{"text":" is a map content source that supplies raster image tiles","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A raster tile source is added to an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"text":" object along with one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer"},{"text":" objects. Use a raster style layer to control the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"appearance of content supplied by the raster tile source.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle/addSource:":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds a new source to the current style."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"addSource:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"addSource:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle\/addsource:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addSource:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize":{"title":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing a floating-point number that specifies the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"width and height (measured in points) at which the map displays each raster"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image tile when the map’s zoom level is an integer. The raster tile source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"scales its images up or down when the map’s zoom level falls between two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"integers."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntilesourceoptiontilesize","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"}],"title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:","role":"symbol"}}}